summary:
With my background in diplomatic affairs, international affairs and business consulting, I wish to blend in into the multinational network of The Netherlands and find my new path here. I am looking for a job which suits this background, my education and which will also be challenging for me as a person.

I am fluent in Russian, Kazakh and English. Currently studying Dutch.
